# """
# Improved DMRL: Counterfactual Sparse Polar Evidence Transport
# for multimodal sentiment analysis.
#
# Compared with the previous version, this implementation makes the model
# more compact and internally consistent for paper submission:
# 1. Modality-specific stems + shared Transformer encoder with lightweight adapters
# 2. Hybrid static + input-adaptive sparse evidence slots
# 3. Strength/uncertainty-aware evidence pooling
# 4. Sinkhorn-style uncertainty-aware evidence transport
# 5. Soft consensus/conflict/residual role decomposition
# 6. Counterfactual router using the same main prediction head for factual and CF predictions
# 7. Ordinal distribution head with predictive variance instead of an extra interval head
# """
